title: Massive Attack - Obelisk
description:
Massive Attack - Obelisk
Bootleg
Compiled in: 12 Sep. 2008

Here is a bootleg collecting a fair amount of rarities from Massive Attack. No remixes of or by other people, no 3D or Sinead O&#039;Connor songs tagged as Massive Attack, no fakes (all the tracks are real, even the Teardrop Call-out Hooks which appear on a US promo of Teardrop single), just MA songs.
Enjoy!
